added.title: The Limo
added.description: To help distract Panda from his girl problems, Grizz and Ice Bear treat him to a ride in a limo.

added.title: More Everyone's Tube
added.description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

added.title: Welcome to Zombozo-Zone!
added.description: During medieval times, Team Tennyson must fight to remember that they're not in the past at all, but actually at a Renaissance-esque faire, where "King Zombozo" has hypnotized its guests into thinking they live in the past!

added.title: Bridge Out
added.description: After an overpass collapses on the highway, Team Tennyson is in a traffic jam along with Simon Sez and family. But when Ben and Simon team up to tackle the gridlock together, Simon only makes matters much, much worse.

added.title: Beach Heads
added.description: After traveling to Tampa Beach, Florida, Team Tennyson hopes to get some much-needed rest & relaxation, but the tempests without a temper, the Weatherheads, have other plans that Ben must thwart: to build a new beach base!

added.title: Charm School's Out
added.description: During a family cookout at a forest campsite, Charmcaster users her magic to switch places with Gwen, but when Ben catches "Charmcaster" sneaking about, he attacks, unaware it's actually his cursed cousin!

added.title: Billy Bajillions
added.description: In Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max are on a hike to find the Forgeti, but when they realize they've stumbled upon Billy Billions own "Winter in July" ski resort, Ben must battle Billy, with an assist from the Forgeti itself.

added.title: Creek Daycare
added.description: Craig and his sister, Jessica, try their hand at running the daycare at the Creek.

added.title: Sugar Smugglers
added.description: Craig, Kelsey and JP become smugglers to sneak candy to kids in need.

added.title: Sleepover at JP's
added.description: JP invites his friends over for a sleepover, but it happens to be on the night of a huge game of Flashlight Tag in the Creek!

added.title: Tea Timer's Ball
added.description: The Tea Timers throw a dance and invite everyone in the Creek. Craig believes it's solely to prank him, while Kelsey deals with an unwanted admirer.

added.title: The Cardboard Identity
added.description: Craig and his friends stumble upon a mysterious bunker made of cardboard beneath the Creek.

added.title: Gobble Head
added.description: Chef accidentally cooks up a killer cyborg turkey in a failed attempt to get the kids to appreciate him on Appreciation Day.

added.title: Ghoul Spirit
added.description: Gwen rejects the friendship of a friendly ghost.

added.title: Duncan Carving
added.description: Duncan takes advantage of a questionable Halloween legend to steal candy from his classmates.

added.title: Tu Ba or Not Tu Ba
added.description: The class tries to help Chef achieve his dream of joining the world's most famous Tuba Band, Tubalicious, only to regret it when they realize how much they'll miss him.

added.title: Dude Where's Macaw
added.description: While trying to defend his elite gamer status Chef uses an old cheat code that brings a dangerous avatar to life.

added.title: Way Back Wendel
added.description: Courtney must deliberately lose a challenge or let the entire world go back in time. It's a really hard choice for her.

added.title: Stingin' in the Rain
added.description: When Chef gets locked outside in a storm, the kids mistakenly assume he's a robber and decide to protect the Daycare, by any means necessary.

added.title: Cartoon Realism
added.description: Gwen is frustrated by Beth's silly belief that cartoons are real, but they visit an animation studio and discover that Beth is right!

added.title: OWW
added.description: When the kids discover Chef's past as a disgraced pro wrestler, they invite his old tag team partner to help put on a charity show. But is the big match about re-union or re-venge?!?

added.title: The Bad Guy Busters
added.description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

added.title: Apple's Formula
added.description: Apple needs to find a funny formula that will land him a comedic in a movie.

added.title: River of Gold
added.description: Apple & Onion try to finish a story before the book disappears forever.

added.title: Appleoni
added.description: Apple and Onion want credit for creating a new dance craze.

added.title: Falafel's in Jail
added.description: Apple & Onion must get Falafel out of jail for a crime he did not commit.

added.title: The Music Store Thief
added.description: Apple and Onion have to defend the music store from instrument theft to get a key to the store.

added.title: Queen of the Munce
added.description: Jay, Nya and Lloyd are led deep into the Mines of Shintaro by Murt, who brings them back to the Munce "Home- Cave" - a settlement deep in the mountain. There, complications arise when they meet the Munce Queen, Murtessa, who takes a liking to Jay.

added.title: Trial By Mino
added.description: Separated from the others, Kai and Zane discover a party of Geckles who suspect them of being in league with the Skull Sorcerer, and bring them before their leader, Chancellor Gulch, who subjects them to a "Trial-By-Mino."

added.title: The Skull Sorcerer
added.description: Separated from the others, Cole must trust his instincts and make the right choices to find his way to the surface to alert King Vangelis of the dangerous Skull Sorcerer.

added.title: The Real Fall!
added.description: An entire episode chronicles the ninja's most bizarre adventure yet: in which Cole, Princess Vania and Master Wu fall down a seemingly endless tunnel, into the bowels of Shintaro Mountain.

added.title: Dungeon Party
added.description: Having survived their fall into the mountain, Cole, Wu and Princess Vania befriend a motley group of survivors, called the Lowly, and are told the story of how they too ended up at "Rock-Bottom."

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 1
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 2
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: #ItsComplicated
added.description: When Hal Jordan sees Carol Ferris with a new boyfriend, his ego can't handle the rejection, resulting in the most absurd Lantern battle ever.

added.title: #SchoolGhoul
added.description: When Tatsu Yamashiro asks for help at a haunted all-girls academy, Barbara Gordon and Kara Danvers find themselves caught up in something much bigger than a ghost hunt.

added.title: Lion-S
added.description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

added.title: Snarf's Day Off
added.description: Hey everyone, it's Snarf's monthly day off! That's right, this episode follows Snarf as he leaves Cats' Lair to get a needed vacation, by transforming into a normal cat and hanging out with a nice old lady on a farm! But his relaxing day is threatened when Snarf and the nice old lady cross paths with Mumm-Ra!

added.title: Log Date 7 15 2
added.description: Steven sneaks a listen to a friend's audio diary.

added.title: Super Watermelon Island
added.description: Steven finds out what happened to all those sentient watermelons he created.

added.title: Gem Drill
added.description: Steven takes a journey deep underground.

added.title: Legend of Torbaclaun
added.description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

added.title: Baost in Show
added.description: When Bao Bao returns, and the King makes him his pet, Mao Mao must rescue his ex-partner.

added.title: Fright Wig
added.description: When the King cannot overcome his fears, he abuses having the Sheriff's Dept. on call.

added.title: Sleeper Sofa
added.description: When the Sky Pirates infiltrate Sheriff HQ, they put our heroes in danger!

added.title: Lucky Ducky Mug
added.description: When Adorabat and Badgerclops break Mao Mao's favorite mug, he gives them the silent treatment.

added.title: Ring of Fire
added.description: When an old flame comes calling on urgent business, Tree Trunks reconsiders both her wild past and her tranquil present.

added.title: Scary Tales 2
added.description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

added.title: Old Lady Bodyguard
added.description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

added.title: Too Cool
added.description: Puppycorn needs a lesson in how to be cool. The gang is more than happy to teach him, until his coolness unexpectedly freezes the whole kingdom.

added.title: La mascara del engano
added.description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: The Mask of Deception
added.description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

added.title: La princesa de jade
added.description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: The Jade Princess
added.description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

added.title: El oni y el dragon
added.description: Mientras que la Princesa Harumi se adapta a la vida con los ninjas, Lloyd y Jay buscan respuestas sobre las máscaras Oni, mientras que Cole y Zane intentan infiltrarse en Los Hijos de Garmadon.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: The Oni & the Dragon
added.description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

added.title: Guar serpiente
added.description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Snake Jaguar
added.description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

added.title: El chillido de hombre muerto
added.description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Dead Man's Squall
added.description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

added.title: La Limosna
added.description: Para ayudar a Panda a distraerse de sus problemas románticos, Pardo y Polar le regalan un paseo en limosina.

added.title: Mas del canal de todos
added.description: A través de otra sesión de navegación por Internet, vemos más videos subidos por los Osos y sus amigos.

added.title: Uncle Melvins
added.description: Legendary rock band, the Melvins, team up with Uncle Grandpa to help a young girl who wants to win her school's talent show.

added.title: Costume Crisis
added.description: Uncle Grandpa makes improvements to a kid's Halloween costume.

added.title: A Sumoful Mind
added.description: When Jeff realizes Sumo's new classes have been rubbing off on Sumo, he attempts to further foster this newfound intellectual Sumo! But will Clarence's lowbrow antics reverse Jeff's hard work?

added.title: Animal Day
added.description: Clarence feels the call of the wild - and decides to live a new life, free of the hustle and bustle of the modern world. Recruiting a few friends, Clarence sets out to find a new place to live his feral life, but quickly realizes he lacks some basic survival skills.

added.title: The Tunnel
added.description: After Clarence accidentally knocks Belson's new video game down a storm drain, Belson enters the large underground sewer tunnel to retrieve it. When Belson doesn't return, Clarence must decide whether or not to go in after him.

added.title: Talent Show
added.description: Clarence throws a big talent show in his yard to showcase all the fun hidden talents of his friends. But when Brady claims he's talentless, Clarence sets out to prove that everyone has something special to share!

added.title: Bienvenido a la Zona Zombozo
added.description: Durante tiempos medievales, el equipo Tennyson debe esforzarse por recordar que no están en el pasado, sino en una feria renacentista, idonde el "Rey Zombozo" ha hipnotizado a sus invitados para que crean que viven en el pasado!

added.title: Bloqueo de Tránsito
added.description: Cuando un paso elevado colapsa sobre la autopista, el equipo Tennyson queda varado en un embotellamiento junto con Simon Sez y familia. Pero cuando Ben y Simon se alían para enfrentar juntos al atasco, Simon solo consigue que las cosas sean mucho, pero mucho peores.

added.title: Cabeza de Playa
added.description: Después de viajar a Tampa Beach, Florida, el equipo Tennyson espera poder descansar y relajarse, pero las tempestades sin temperamento, los Climáticos, tienen otros planes que Ben debe frustrar: iconstruir una nueva base en la playa!

added.title: Encantadas
added.description: Durante una comida familiar en un campamento forestal, Charmcaster usa su magia para cambiar de lugar con Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre a "Charmcaster" husmeando, ataca, sin darse cuenta de que en realidad es su hechizada prima.

added.title: Billy Billones
added.description: En Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max van de excursión para encontrar al Olvideti. Pero cuando se encuentran con la pista artificial de esquí de Billy Billones, Ben debe luchar contra Billy con la ayuda del propio Olvideti.

added.title: The Judge Part 1
added.description: The Quintesson Judge and his forces assault Iaconus while Optimus and Megatron lead a strike team into the Quintesson ship.

added.title: The Judge Part 2
added.description: Megatron and Optimus's strike team faces off against the Scientist while the Autobot and Decepticon defenders of Iaconus desperately keep the all-powerful Judge distracted.

added.title: The End of the Universe I Part 1
added.description: Starscream's fate at the hands of the Quintessons is revealed as he returns a three-headed Judge!

added.title: The End of the Universe I Part 2
added.description: Judge Starscream interrogates his Cybetronian prisoners while Optimus, Bee, and Wheeljack try to get back through the Multiverse Bridge.

added.title: The End of the Universe II Part 1
added.description: Windblade battles the Sharkticons to regain entry into Iaconus.

added.title: The End of the Universe II Part 2
added.description: While the Autobots and Decepticons stall Judge Starscream, Windblade tries to awaken Iaconus.

added.title: Breaking Bliss
added.description: When Bliss struggles to control her powers an evil force arises to take advantage.

added.title: All in the Villainy
added.description: KO, Rad and Enid are confused to find the villains are more interested in battling each other than them.

added.title: Sidekick Scouts
added.description: KO gets more than he bargained for when he gets a sidekick.

added.title: Whacky Jaxxyz
added.description: When the hot new toy trend of Whacky Jaxxyz comes to Lakewood, KO says goodbye to his POW Cards.

added.title: Midnight at the Mayor's Mansion
added.description: When the Mayor's mansion is stalked by a vicious, ghostly monster, he calls the Powerpuff Girls for help.

added.title: Project Ray Way
added.description: When Raymond starts his own fashion line, Rad and Drupe decide to make something even better.

added.title: La identidad de carton
added.description: Craig y sus amigos se topan con un refugio subterráneo hecho de cartón debajo del bosque.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Contrabandistas de Azucar
added.description: Craig, Kelsey y JP se convierten en contrabandistas para llevarle dulces a niños necesitados.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Pijamada en casa de JP
added.description: JP invita a sus amigos para una pijamada, pero resulta ser la misma noche que un gran juego con linternas en el Arroyo.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Ayudantes Scouts
added.description: KO obtiene más de lo que esperaba cuando consigue su propio ayudante.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: Mi Villana Familia
added.description: KO, Rad y Enid se sienten confundidos cuando descubren que los villanos están más interesados en enfrentarse entre sí que en enfrentarlos a ellos.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: El baile de los Infusionistas
added.description: Los Infusionistas organizan un baile e invitan a todos los habitantes del bosque. Craig cree que el único propósito del baile es hacerle una broma a él, mientras que Kelsey debe lidiar con un admirador indeseado.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Whacky Jaxxyz
added.description: Cuando Whacky Jaxxyz, el nuevo juego de moda, llega a Lakewoood, KO se despide de sus tarjetas de poder.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
added.description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #LaDulceJusticia - Segunda parte
added.description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 2 del episodio estreno.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Tourist Trap
added.description: While messing with the World's Largest Rubberband Ball at a tourist trap, Ben accidently releases some mischievous electrical creatures.

added.title: Kevin 11
added.description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

added.title: Hard Times in Silicon City
added.description: Mega Man must stop Blasto Woman from plundering the Museum of the Hard Age and its cache of military grade weaponry.

added.title: Tripping the Light Fantastic
added.description: Mega Man tries to save Dr. Light from a date with "Mari," who's actually Hypno Woman in disguise!

added.title: Running Wild
added.description: Student elections get blown out of proportion (literally) when Air Man lends his support to Aki's rival for class president, Peter Punk.

added.title: Unfriendly Competition
added.description: Aki must set aside a petty rivalry with Bert Wily in order to stop Chemistry Man from wreaking havoc at Silicon Central's Field Day.

added.title: Los Caza Chicos Malos
added.description: Izzqy quiere jugar un juego de superhéroes y está dispuesta a hacer lo que sea por ello.

added.title: Opposites Attract
added.description: Fire Man and Wave Man team up to evaporate the city's water supply, forcing Mega Man to team up with an ally of his own- Suna.

added.title: Mystery, Incorporeal
added.description: An old enemy emerges while Ben and Rook visit Kevin and Gwen at college.

added.title: An American Benwolf in London
added.description: Ben and Rook are called to London England to investigate the Forever Knights' latest activities.

added.title: El joven y la logica
added.description: K.O. descubre cómo el Sr. Lógica llegó a la Plaza.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: Lad & Logic
added.description: KO learns the story of how Mr. Logic came to the plaza.

added.title: Rad Monster Party
added.description: Ben and Rook enlist the help of intergalactic smuggler Rad Dudesman to fly them through the Anur System, the home of the monstrous aliens!

added.title: Collect This
added.description: Ben finally meets the ones responsible for his intergalactic TV show, and the actor who makes Ben 10 more famous than Ben himself!

added.title: La Taza del Patito de la Suerte
added.description: Cuando Adorabat y Colosal rompen la taza favorita de Mao Mao, el sheriff los castiga con su silencio.

added.title: Peluca de Terror
added.description: Cuando el rey no logra superar sus miedos, se abusa de la ventaja que le da tener al departamento del sheriff de guardia.

added.title: Rio de Oro
added.description: Manzana y Cebolla intentan terminar un cuento antes de que el libro desaparezca para siempre.

added.title: Presumir en el Concurso
added.description: Cuando Bao Bao regresa y el rey lo convierte en su mascota, Mao Mao debe rescatar a su antiguo compañero.

added.title: Falafel en la Carcel
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín deben sacar a Falafel de la cárcel por un delito que no cometió.

added.title: El Ladron de Musica
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín tienen que defender la tienda de música del robo de instrumentos para conseguir una llave de la tienda.

added.title: Sofa Cama
added.description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se infiltran en el cuartel general del sheriff, iponen en peligro a los héroes!

added.title: Manzallin
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren llevarse el crédito de haber creado una nueva moda de baile.

added.title: La Formula de Manzana
added.description: Manzana necesita encontrar una fórmula divertida que le permita conseguir un papel cómico en una película.

added.title: La Leyenda del Torbaclaun
added.description: Cuando los Corazoncitos creen que el mítico Torbaclaun ha llegado al Valle Puro Corazón, Mao Mao intenta demostrarles que no es real.

removed.title: Saving Faith
removed.description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

removed.title: Drilling Deep
removed.description: At school, Aki struggles with the side effects of his newly replicated Drill Man schematics; later, as Mega Man, he learns to control his Fire Powers in thwarting Drill Man's assault on Skyraisers Inc.

removed.title: El eslabon mas debil
removed.description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.
removed.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

removed.title: Omni-Copped
removed.description: When Grandpa Max's engineer buddy Phil Billings gifts Team Tennyson the Omni-Copter, a state of the art flying vehicle that can transport the Rustbucket for overseas adventures, Steam Smythe takes to the skies to ground Ben and company's first test flight; but unbeknownst to our heroes, Smythe was sent to battle Ben's latest alien forms by a mysterious, powerful enemy: the Forever Knight.

removed.title: The Scientist Part 2
removed.description: While Hot Rod and Soundwave battle the indestructible Scientist, Perceptor and the rest of the team attempt a mass breakout from the Loop.

removed.title: Videodrone

removed.title: Poles Apart

removed.title: Grown Up Stuff
removed.description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

removed.title: The Weakest Link
removed.description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

removed.title: Rath of Con

removed.title: No lo digas y Hazlo

removed.title: Nice on Ice

removed.title: Omnicoptero
removed.description: Cuando el ingeniero Phil Billings, amigo del Abuelo Max, le regala al equipo Tennyson el Omni-Copter, un vehículo volador de última generación que puede transportar el Rustbucket hasta aventuras en el extranjero, Vapor Smythe sube a los cielos para obligar a aterrizar el primer vuelo de prueba de Ben y su familia. removed.title: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call/Phantom Thief Ajit

removed.title: Los Jovenes Titanes Salvan la Navidad
removed.description: Santa renuncia a la Navidad, y los Titanes deben intervenir para salvar la festividad.
